Package: knx-installer
Architecture: all
Depends: dialog, initrd-tools, perl, bash (>>2.05), lilo, kdm, grub-gfxboot | grub, whois, yaird, kanotix-udev-config
Suggests: gparted, xdialog, distro-defaults, 855resolution
Conflicts: ifrename
Description: installs kanotix to hd
 kanotix-installer is an fully functional installation program
 to easily install kanotix to hd. It has support for config-files, 
 which allow more advanced usages.

